  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this trial is to study the effects of different combinations of antiemetics on
      the incidence of late onset postoperative nausea and vomiting.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The authors will study the effect of many antiemetics on the occurrence of nausea and
      vomiting following strabismus surgery in pediatrics.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
